@startuml DFD Level 0 Context
!theme plain
skinparam rectangle {
  BackgroundColor White
}

title Level 0 DFD (Context Diagram)

actor "Student" as Student
actor "Recruiter" as Recruiter

rectangle "StudentHub\nCore System" as System #lightblue

Student --> System : Registration Info, Profile Data,\nAssessment Answers, Applications
System --> Student : Learning Paths, Job Recommendations,\nInterview Invites, Skill Feedback

Recruiter --> System : Job Requirements, Interview Schedules,\nCandidate Feedback, Company Data
System --> Recruiter : Ranked Candidates, Analytics,\nMatched Profiles, Application Status

@enduml
